title: "Real World/Road Rules Challenge: Impeachment Inferno."
description: The House of Representatives votes to endorse the impeachment inquiry into Donald Trump, a parade of the President’s employees testify against him, and the Democratic candidates descend on Des Moines for the biggest event of the Iowa caucuses.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
